<div class="w-full">
  <% content_for :title, "Dashboard" %>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 sm:mb-0">Welcome Back</h1>
    <br/>
    Great progress! You're making a positive impact
    <br/><br/>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-8">
      <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <div class="text-3xl font-semibold text-blue-600"><%= @clients_count %></div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Lives Touched</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <div class="text-3xl font-semibold text-blue-600"><%= @hours_count %></div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Coaching Hours</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <div class="text-3xl font-semibold text-blue-600"><%= @sessions_count %></div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Sessions</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <div class="text-3xl font-semibold text-blue-600"><%= @sessions_paid %>%</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Time Compensated</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    Keep up the fantastic work! Every session brings you closer to your goals.

    <div class="bg-white mt-4 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-2">Ready for ICF Certification?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Streamline your journey with our ICF-compatible coaching log template</p>

      <%= button_to clients_path(format: :xlsx), method: :get, class: "inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-md transition-colors" do %>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
        </svg>
        Download Excel Template
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
